org.gitlab.api

Class GitlabProject.Query

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gitlab.api.GitlabProject.Query
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    GitlabProject.UserQuery
    Enclosing class:
    GitlabProject

    public static class GitlabProject.Query
extends java.lang.Object
    This extends GitlabQuery and supports query global projects. Build this query with setters and call query() to execute query.

    Gitlab Web API: https://docs.gitlab.com/ee/api/projects.html#list-all-projects

    GET /projects
